The second thing that we can do to be effective witnesses in offering hope and healing to our city, to the city of St. Louis is we need to be practicing biblical stewardship.

20:14.600 --> 20:23.889
Proverbs chapter three, verses nine to 10 says, honor the Lord with your wealth and with the best part of everything you produce.

20:24.369 --> 20:29.554
Then he will fill your barns with grain and your vats will overflow with good wine.

20:30.626 --> 20:33.589
We call this the principle of the first fruits.

20:34.750 --> 20:39.415
Biblical stewardship begins with honoring God with our first fruits.

20:40.976 --> 20:49.184
This means giving God the first and the best of our resources, acknowledging that everything we have is from Him.

20:49.965 --> 20:53.468
Guys, if we can make sure the computer sound is on for this next video.

20:55.430 --> 20:57.232
We've seen this video before.

20:58.013 --> 20:59.154
We've played it during

20:59.682 --> 21:07.833
offering time, but I think it provides the best teaching I've seen in a long time on this subject of first fruits.

21:07.873 --> 21:15.684
